{"tid":1104482,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣志光 以前有幾首都唔錯 (^_^)","createTime":"2019-04-13T07:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T13:10:13.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"53fbf9dc3ecf8bfaac6fa2cfaab17ce57f2e8b1f","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fzta50c_G5Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffzta50c_G5Y&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=5cf7aa55\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fzta50c_G5Y</a><br />\n<br />\n音樂工廠我覺得唔係皇后大道東，而係另一首 長路有多遠  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0987538d2861cda77918e4739ee6992189f3fd78","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:32:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d-JXuS0JpPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd-JXuS0JpPI&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=013ef66b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d-JXuS0JpPI</a><br />\n<br />\n新風雲年代  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f643728cbf8bac08401e17e8e5c91bfed72beb16","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1IzCUkSXuL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1IzCUkSXuL8&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=e50527de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1IzCUkSXuL8</a><br />\n<br />\n黃耀光本想找蔣志光合組Raidas，但因他已簽了寶麗金旗下歌手，只好轉找陳德彰，於是蔣志光成了Raidas的隱形成員。<br />\n<br />\n拯救行動星黃耀光的作品，另一首〈你係我邊個〉也是，蔣志光說過黃耀光是他的音樂啟蒙者。"},{"pid":"d75a6020dca15980b22dabfc4012fd5df5e9b7cc","tid":1104482,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"舊朋友 心緊扣"},{"pid":"11b62d302e8370a49d08e0ccf6016a213bd37c14","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QlFrXHgQeLg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQlFrXHgQeLg&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=b63b7de5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QlFrXHgQeLg</a><br />\n<br />\n武俠劇  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8861d8a0ba65e7a97f21ad949716195763791ca","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊朋友 心緊扣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/krBHzmPo6E4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkrBHzmPo6E4&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=3df00e0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/krBHzmPo6E4</a><br />\n<br />\n好奇查吓歷年樂壇新人蒸發實錄<br />\n甘子暉去左邊<br />\n<br />\n1992 甘子暉：與飛圖群星合唱〈舊朋友〉，專輯只有「換季情人」。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知係咪退出左樂壇 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87d86dd000e75ab99b95c7d9c1d505f070d1f5a5","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"