=fc9b7660\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yK39QmSGaJk</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2A2x2ybtLL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2A2x2ybtLL8&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=97eaa41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2A2x2ybtLL8</a><br />\n<br />\n要走的始終都要走 (1990)<br />\n<br />\n一星期叱咤榜冠軍，早過相逢何必曾相識上榜，不過後來被&quot;相逢&quot;鋒頭蓋過，記得這首第一主打的人不多，歌曲結尾的英文和音是韋綺姍，她原本幫監製王利名唱廣告歌，聲靚獲賞識唱和音，要走的始終都要走派台時DJ好奇打聽女和音是誰，監製立刻安排韋綺姍和蔣志光合唱相逢何必曾相識，造就這對經典合唱組合，和這首經典合唱歌。"},{"pid":"2ae89f6ceb4750eea09ecfba36dcde3e9824b99e","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KIIiK3WID6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKIIiK3WID6g&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=407f4da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KIIiK3WID6g</a><br />\n<br />\n唔錯  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8613422116ef2ef75fa6641ecc313d61fa4fc16e","tid":1104482,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"點唧，冇人喜歡我的蔣志光特輯嗎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ce4264